snippet.title: A.I. A New Kind of Love Prologue
snippet.description:
It seemed intriguing at first, but then I tried the prologue and it lost some of its appeal. So far I adore the robot maid, but I'll be giving it a try. Will be starting off w/ Asano. Depending on how it goes, I''ll do Sanada next and Roy last.

Seriously though RobotMaid is best girl, and I love her sassiness. She's like the best of the prologue/chapter 1!
